---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="About nologin.tools — a curated directory of tools that work without login.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">About nologin.tools</h1>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-950 mb-3">Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We believe the best tools respect your time and privacy. <strong>nologin.tools</strong> is
          a curated directory of software and services that let you get things done without creating
          an account or handing over personal information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-950 mb-3">How It Works</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>Anyone can <a href="/submit" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">submit a tool</a> they believe works without login.</li>
          <li>Our team reviews each submission to verify the no-login claim.</li>
          <li>Approved tools receive the <strong>NoLogin Verified</strong> badge and appear in the public directory.</li>
          <li>The community can suggest edits to keep information accurate (wiki mode).</li>
          <li>We continuously monitor tool availability with automated health checks.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-950 mb-3">NoLogin Verified Badge</h2>
        <p>
          The <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-green-600 font-medium">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
              <circle cx="7" cy="7" r="7" fill="#22c55e"/>
              <path d="M4 7L6 9L10 5" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            NoLogin Verified
          </span> badge means we have confirmed that a tool's core functionality is accessible
          without registration or login. Tool creators can display this badge on their own sites —
          <a href="/badge" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">learn more</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-950 mb-3">Open Source</h2>
        <p>
          nologin.tools is open source and built with Astro, Cloudflare Workers, and D1.
          All verified tools are also exported to an
          <a href="https://github.com/nologin-tools" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
            awesome-nologin-tools
          </a> list on GitHub.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
